reviews.review_text: ? Why are these shows being reseeded, I thought that there were already links to the SHN files on the old sources? Is this a new source? Whats up? Anyone.....?
4-23-84 This is a good show. If you can't tolerate tape hiss leave this one alone. It has better sound than the other boards thanks to Charlie.
First show This was my first show!!! OMG I wish I was more in tune then. No wonder why I have stayed loyal all these years. The boys sure did real me in. I just love listening over and over.
4-23-84 New Haven Ct Even though I was backstage and was in the 3rd row, I have to say I remember not being impressed with this show. However......The next night was AWSOME
Sugaree It's a pretty good one for 84!
